olsrv2TibAdNeighborSetAddrType OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX InetAddressType MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The type of the olsrv2TibAdNeighborSetAddr, as defined in the InetAddress MIB [RFC 4001]." REFERENCE "The OLSRv2 draft." ::= { olsrv2TibAdNeighborSetEntry 2 }
