olsrv2TibAdRemoteNodeSetIndex OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Unsigned32 (1..65535) UNITS "" MAX-ACCESS not-accessible STATUS current DESCRIPTION "This object is an additional index for each Remote Node's IfAddr associated with the olsrv2TibAdRemoteNodeSetAddr." REFERENCE "The OLSRv2 draft." ::= { olsrv2TibAdRemoteNodeSetEntry 3 }
